    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 is a masterclass in mechanical preservation. Featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, the engine exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders with the dual-VANOS system meticulously serviced. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise six-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis has been proactively reinforced at the subframe\u2014a critical preventative measure\u2014and upgraded with Bilstein dampers for sharpened turn-in response. Clad in its original factory paint with a mirror-like finish, the interior remains immaculate with supple Nappa leather and crisp switchgear. This is a turnkey, high-performance icon for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
