    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle in showroom condition. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior paint is flawless, featuring a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are no stone chips, swirl marks, or blemishes to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, retaining its original factory scent. The premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear or bolster compression, and every electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is perfect, backed by a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. All original keys, manuals, and service records are included. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a 'time capsule' example that satisfies even the most discerning enthusiast.",
